topsbot_yolo_det
Copyright 2026 TOPSBOT contributors

This product includes YOLO detection nodes and inference helpers for TOPSBOT MES20 boards.

Implementation references the TOPSBOT model-zoo YOLO sample pipelines for preprocessing,
postprocessing, and NPU runtime usage.

YOLO model files (.nb) are not distributed with this repository; see scripts/download_models.sh
and config/models_manifest.yaml.
